{'summary_text': 'Tommaso got a new laptop today. He has problems with the e-mail sign-up. He asks Tomas to create him an outlOOK EMAIL SIGNATURE for his new laptop. He will use the account of the account he created. '}

{'summary_text': "Grazie can't open a ticket for support, because of an error in the Outlook.com website. Buongiorno helps her to upload her personal photo to the Outlook website and sends her a link to a website with an Outlook sign-up code."}
